1. *Pakao* je zaista mesto za koje niko nikada ne želi da čuje (Hell is truly a place that nobody ever wants to hear about).

2. Njegova glupost me je dovela do *pakla* (His stupidity brought me to hell). 

3. Da li će on biti proklet večno u *paklu*? (Will he be cursed forever in hell?). 

4. Ona je predstavljala *pakao* koji se nalazi u njenoj glavi (She represented the hell that lies in her head). 

5. *Pakleno* vreme je trajalo puna tri godine (The hellish time lasted full three years). 

6. Ona je umrla sa *paklenom* bolom (She died with hellish pain).